Class BooleanBooleanMutablePair

java.lang.Object
it.unimi.dsi.fastutil.booleans.BooleanBooleanMutablePair
All Implemented Interfaces:
BooleanBooleanPair, Pair<Boolean,Boolean>, Serializable
public class BooleanBooleanMutablePair extends Object implements BooleanBooleanPair, Serializable
A type-specific mutable Pair; provides some additional methods that use polymorphism to avoid (un)boxing.
